This HI-III-20 dataset contains over 52,000 PPIs involving more than 8,000 proteins.

Author: Gordon DE (2020)
Qualifications: High confidence interactions were identified using a two step filtering process with the final criteria including a MiST score >= 0.6, SAINTexpress BFDR =< 0.05 and average spectral counts >= 2. The MiST score is provided in the score column.
